{"type": "article", "id": 30811, "title": "蛋白粉包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-09T23:01:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160809233346aVAtLBkeuvP926nG.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>蛋白粉品牌 Iron-Tek 最近委托 <a href=\"http://beardwood.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Beardwood &amp; Co.</a> 重新设计了自己的 LOGO、产品包装以及网页。在主视觉上，他们在翻阅历史资料之后选择了 Harold Von Schmidt 绘制的海报，画面中的工人形象传递出自然而健康的阳刚气质。海报下方则是具有现代感的信息图，让顾客能够直观地了解到品牌的功效。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233636DSCJx7WjPXVbudFo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.283364\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233636j8HM07I2FVTf3zbU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.288848\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233441QYsbKGk428ajcJ3p.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.466844\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809233441DAsZdQNgWpc4aJYO.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.526000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}